Package gameTools

Class Leaderboard

java.lang.Object
gameTools.Leaderboard
public class Leaderboard extends Object

Loads and updates the leaderboard that tracks the fastest times to complete the game.

April 11, 2024
Author:

  • Field Details

    • levels

      public static final Map<Integer,Leaderboard> levels
      Map that stores the leaderboard for each level. The key represents the level leaderboard. So 1 corresponds to level 1 leaderboard, 2 to level 2 leaderboard. 3 corresponds to the overall leaderboard, because level three is the last level, so beating it would be beating the game.

    • fileName

      private final String fileName
      Stores the file name for the leaderboard file.

    • leaderboardName

      private String leaderboardName
      Stores the name of the leaderboard, which is the first line of the file.
